{"root":{"data":{"id":"d80cor0q0ww0","created":1740367210345,"text":"指标体系"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cpig3h5k0","created":1740367270048,"text":"指标体系有什么用？"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cpsbpupk0","created":1740367291551,"text":"业务观测"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cpw2i85s0","created":1740367299701,"text":"完整观测业务全貌，避免聚焦局部"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d80cq1l5ncw0","created":1740367311713,"text":"从各角度进行观测，避免片面结论、无效结论"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80cqb6dlxc0","created":1740367332587,"text":"商业决策"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cqddx24o0","created":1740367337396,"text":"统一数据语言"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cqhsu5v40","created":1740367347006,"text":"1、找准目标，检测业务进度"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d80cqkxnvc00","created":1740367353828,"text":"2、发现机会点与问题点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d80cqoaqsqo0","created":1740367361149,"text":"3、评估项目生命周期，及后续资源投入"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80cr1qi7kw0","created":1740367390400,"text":"备注：指标体系是业务观测、决策的载体、工具，但不是物理数据表"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80crjxgayo0","created":1740367430002,"text":"指标体系两大要素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80crnl94140","created":1740367437972,"text":"业务理解"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80crsrsuo80","created":1740367449252,"text":"找核心矛盾，避免南辕北辙、次优化"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80croqqkrk0","created":1740367440480,"text":"体系化思考"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80crx0d8q00","created":1740367458477,"text":"准确设计指标的层次结构，支撑高效分析、监控"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80csk6zqnc0","created":1740367508943,"text":"指标体系设计常见问题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cso3w9ts0","created":1740367517463,"text":"业务理解优、体系化思考差——难以有序分析：指标体系不完整；眉毛胡子一把抓，过于复杂、缺乏结构","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cxe3c5r40","created":1740367887483,"text":"Bad case：指标过于平铺、缺乏结构"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d80cv8k9o5k0","created":1740367718717,"text":"业务理解差、体系化思考优——业务失败风险高：可能导致项目次优化或失败；由于具备分层分类，在实际工作中具有迷惑性","layout_right_offset":{"x":44,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d80cydf8z1s0","created":17403679643